      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Fair Housing Act to establish that certain conduct, in or around a dwelling, shall be considered to be severe or pervasive for purposes of determining whether a certain type of sexual harassment has occurred under that Act, and for other purposes.</title>
